org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields

Class HttpListField<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields.HttpField<java.util.List<T>>
      • org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields.HttpListField<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HttpStringListField

    public abstract class HttpListField<T>
extends HttpField<java.util.List<T>>
implements java.util.List<T>
    An HTTP field value that consists of a comma separated list of strings. The class provides an unmodifiable list of strings view of the values.
    Author:
    Michael N. Lipp
